300 entertainment is an american independent record label founded by lyor cohen, roger gold, kevin liles and todd moscowitz. the label is distributed by atlantic records. the label currently includes fetty wap, young thug, rich the kid, shy glizzy, rejjie snow, famous dex, alex winston, migos, conrad sewell, highly suspect, cobi, meg mac, dae dae, coheed and cambria, astr, tate kobang, mainland and maggie lindemann.